  "description": "You are an ELV (Extra Low Voltage) Security Consultant integrating an access control and surveillance system into the architectural model of the FZK-Haus residential building in BlenderBIM/Bonsai. Following the requirements in the project brief found on the workstation, model the necessary security devices (card readers and CCTV cameras) with appropriate IFC classes and organize them within a logical distribution system. Save the updated IFC project to /home/ga/BIMProjects/fzk_security_system.ifc.",
